<div class="welcome">
  <h2>Welcome to Better Self</h2>
  <p>Here at Better Self, we pride ourselves on being "life longs students". That's why I developed this application in the first place! To share concepts and information with like minded individuals. Whether it be fitness, health, wealth, business, social skills, mindfulness, and more. You can find it all here!</p>
</div>

{{#each posts }}
<div class="homepage-cards row mb-4 post">
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <h2>
      <a class="post-name" href="/post/{{id}}">{{name}}</a>
    </h2>
    <p class="post-info">Posted by <span class="homepage-cards-username">{{user.name}}</span> on {{format_date date_created}}</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <p>{{description}}</p>
  </div>
</div>
{{/each}}